description	"Shaak Ti

^2Weaponry:
- Shaak Ti's Lightsaber
-- ^3Yellow ^7/ ^1Red ^7/ ^4Blue ^7Styles
-- Saber Defense   (3)
-- Blaster Defense (2)
-- Blaster Deflect (1)

^5Force Powers:
