- Sense (2) ^5[CS4]

^8Attributes:
- Cannot Pickup Weapons
- Force Block (2)

Surprisingly for someone from the race of the Togruta, Jedi Master Shaak Ti was best known for her independent spirit. After losing both of her Padawans to criminal killers, the exotic alien female with colorful patterning decorating her flexible lekku, is now travelling alone."